# Overview

This submission presents an **AI-powered Employee Onboarding Automation System** built using **n8n** and **Large Language Models (LLMs)**.

The solution automates employee onboarding by validating employee information, generating personalized onboarding plans, creating welcome emails, and maintaining onboarding records and audit logs.

The objective is to reduce manual HR effort while improving onboarding consistency, accuracy, and employee experience.

